thread.title_full: China Jan-Sept non-financial outbound direct investment rises 16.5 pct on year - Xinhua | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: China Jan-Sept non-financial outbound direct investment rises 16.5 pct on year - Xinhua
text:
BEIJING Oct 15 China's non-financial outbound direct investment (ODI) rose 16.5 percent to $87.3 billion in the first three quarters of 2015 compared with the same period last year, state media agency Xinhua reported on Thursday, citing the Ministry of Commerce.
(Reporting by Meng Meng and Nicholas Heath; Editing by Kim Coghill)
